 supreme court of western australia and sue robertssmith his brother sam is an opera singer who graduated from the western australian academy of performing arts and from  into  sang with the ten tenors honours and awardsedit medals on display at the australian war memorial note that this display does not include his full entitlement robertssmith was named australian father of the year in  ribbon description notes victoria cross for australia for most conspicuous gallantry in action in circumstances of extreme peril on  june  while deployed on operation slipper afghanistan medal for gallantry for gallantry in action in hazardous circumstances as a patrol sniper while deployed on operation slipper afghanistan may–september  commendation for distinguished service for distinguished performance of duty in warlike operations as a patrol commander with the special operations task group on operation slipper australian active service medal with clasps for east timor icat and iraq  international force east timor medal interfet afghanistan medal operation slipper iraq medal operation catalyst australian service medal with clasp for ctsr counter terrorism  special recovery queen elizabeth ii diamond jubilee medal  defence long service medal for  years service australian defence medal united nations medal with unamet ribbon for active service in timorleste east timor nato medal for the nonarticle  isaf operation in afghanistan with isaf clasp unit citation for gallantry with federation star  meritorious unit citation with federation star special operations task group task force  infantry combat badge referencesedit  dodd mark  january  second sas afghan victoria cross for heroic charge the australian news limited archived from the original on  january  retrieved  january    a b aap  january  victoria cross for soldier who tore into taliban herald sun news limited retrieved  january    aap  january  sas digger awarded vc for taking on taliban the sydney morning herald fairfax med